<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="on-trial">on trial</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>在试用中；在受审：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He’s <strong>on trial for</strong> theft. 
他因盗窃而受审。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The clerk was employed on trial. 
那位职员在试用期中。</p></div></div>